Package: splicing
Type: Package
Title: Various functions to study alternative splicing.
Version: @@@@@@@@@@ missing @@@@@@@@@@
Date: @@@@@@@@@@ missing @@@@@@@@@@
Author: Gabor Csardi <gcsardi@stat.harvard.edu>
Maintainer: Gabor Csardi <gcsardi@stat.harvard.edu>
Suggests: RCurl, snow
Description: Various functions to study alternative splicing.
  Most importantly, the package contains a fast implementation 
  of the Mixture of Isoforms (MISO) isoform quantitation algorithm.
  It also supports gene visualization, checking whether
  isoform expression levels can be calculated for a given gene 
  structure, and a novel gene structure complexity measure.
